InitBlock.name: PREVIOUS_YEAR

DBMapItem.name: DefaultMulDB
DBMapItem.Value: SELECT PRV.CAL_YEAR, PRV.PER_NAME_MONTH, PRV.PER_NAME_FSCL_MNTH, PRV.PER_NAME_FSCL_QTR FROM VALUEOF(OLAPTBO).W_DAY_D PRV , VALUEOF(OLAPTBO).W_DAY_D CUR WHERE to_char(PRV.DAY_DT,'yyyymmdd')=to_char(CUR.YEAR_AGO_DT - VALUEOF(TIME_OFFSET),'yyyymmdd') and to_char(CUR.DAY_DT,'yyyymmdd')=to_char(SYSDATE - VALUEOF(TIME_OFFSET),'yyyymmdd')
